Reference:
  - 'Application Monitoring in Java with New Relic (Free Setup)' by Integrations Ninjas
  - https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=swpi7EVsVhc

Notes:
 - This project is an independent Spring Boot application used to demonstrate New Relic monitoring.
 - No New Relic dependency is added to the application.
 - Monitoring is enabled using the New Relic Java Agent.
 - Sample Order CRUD APIs are implemented using in-memory storage (ConcurrentHashMap).
 - Preloaded sample order data is available when the application starts.
 - Simulated latency is added to generate meaningful transaction traces and performance metrics in New Relic.
 - Spring Boot Actuator is optional and is not required for New Relic monitoring.
 - Running the Application with New Relic Agent
   java -javaagent:D:/dev/github/springboot-newrelic/newrelic-java/newrelic/newrelic.jar -jar target/springboot-newrelic-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar


Create New Relic Key:
 - License key:
   User Profile > API Keys > Create a Key > Key Type = Ingest - License; Name =  springboot-newrelic > Create a Key > Copy the Key
   
   4e66*******NRAL

Steps to configure:
 - Download 'New Relic agent' zip file
   URL: https://download.newrelic.com/newrelic/java-agent/newrelic-agent/9.3.0/
   Zip File:  newrelic-java.zip

 - Copy 'newrelic-java.zip' zip file to project root folder and extract

 - Update the below fields in 'newrelic-java/newrelic.yml' file
   license_key: '291e*******NRAL'
   app_name: springboot-newrelic

   development:
     <<: *default_settings
     app_name: springboot-newrelic (Development)

   test:
     <<: *default_settings
     app_name: springboot-newrelic (Test)

   production:
     <<: *default_settings

   staging:
     <<: *default_settings
     app_name: springboot-newrelic (Staging)


Commands:
 cd D:\dev\github\springboot-newrelic>
 mvn clean install
 java -javaagent:D:/dev/github/springboot-newrelic/newrelic-java/newrelic/newrelic.jar -jar target/springboot-newrelic-0.0.1-SNAPSHOT.jar


NRQL (New Relic Query Language):

     SELECT * from Transaction

     | ---------------------- | ----------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
     | Category               | Purpose                       | NRQL Query                                                                                |
     | ---------------------- | ----------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
     | Transaction Count      | Total requests processed      |  SELECT count(*) FROM Transaction SINCE 1 hour ago                                        |
     | Average Response Time  | Average API latency           |  SELECT average(duration) FROM Transaction SINCE 1 hour ago                               |
     | P95 / P99 Latency      | Tail latency analysis         |  SELECT percentile(duration, 95, 99) FROM Transaction SINCE 1 hour ago                    |
     | Requests by Endpoint   | Traffic per endpoint          |  SELECT count(*) FROM Transaction FACET name SINCE 1 hour ago                             |
     | Slowest Endpoints      | Find slow APIs                |  SELECT average(duration) FROM Transaction FACET name SINCE 1 hour ago LIMIT 10           |
     | Throughput (RPM)       | Requests per minute           |  SELECT rate(count(*), 1 minute) FROM Transaction SINCE 1 hour ago                        |
     | Throughput by Endpoint | RPM per API                   |  SELECT rate(count(*), 1 minute) FROM Transaction FACET name SINCE 1 hour ago             |
     | Transaction Details    | View transaction events       |  SELECT * FROM Transaction LIMIT 100                                                      |
     | Slowest Transactions   | Find slow requests            |  SELECT name, duration FROM Transaction ORDER BY duration DESC LIMIT 20                   |
     | Order APIs Only        | Filter specific APIs          |  SELECT * FROM Transaction WHERE request.uri LIKE '/api/orders%' LIMIT 100                |
     | Error Count            | Total application errors      |  SELECT count(*) FROM TransactionError SINCE 1 hour ago                                   |
     | Error Rate             | Percentage of failed requests |  SELECT percentage(count(*), WHERE error IS true) FROM Transaction SINCE 1 hour ago       |
     | Errors by Exception    | Most common exceptions        |  SELECT count(*) FROM TransactionError FACET error.class SINCE 1 hour ago                 |
     | Heap Memory Usage      | JVM heap consumption          |  SELECT average(heapUsed) FROM JavaVirtualMachineSample SINCE 1 hour ago                  |
     | GC Time                | Garbage Collection overhead   |  SELECT average(gcCpuTime) FROM JavaVirtualMachineSample SINCE 1 hour ago                 |
     | Thread Count           | JVM thread monitoring         |  SELECT average(threadCount) FROM JavaVirtualMachineSample SINCE 1 hour ago               |
     | CPU Usage              | Server CPU utilization        |  SELECT average(cpuPercent) FROM SystemSample SINCE 1 hour ago                            |
     | Memory Usage           | Server memory utilization     |  SELECT average(memoryUsedBytes/memoryTotalBytes)*100 FROM SystemSample SINCE 1 hour ago  |
     | Apdex Score            | User satisfaction metric      |  SELECT apdex(duration, t:0.5) FROM Transaction SINCE 1 hour ago                          |
     | ---------------------- | ----------------------------- | ----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |

Common NRQL's:

     | ---------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------- |
     | Question                                 | Query                                                               |
     | ---------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------- |
     | How much traffic is my service handling? | SELECT count(*) FROM Transaction                                    |
     | Which API is slow?                       | SELECT average(duration) FROM Transaction FACET name                |
     | What is the worst-case latency?          | SELECT percentile(duration, 95, 99) FROM Transaction                |
     | Are users seeing failures?               | SELECT percentage(count(*), WHERE error IS true) FROM Transaction   |
     | What exceptions are occurring?           | SELECT count(*) FROM TransactionError FACET error.class             |
     | ---------------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------- |
